    "title": "零基础彩铅教程（9）-狐狸先生小插画",
    "leassonType": 1,
    "html": "<p>今天来画一只可爱的狐狸先生</p><p>先献上成品</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0HstIpVaq8CMAuiavGh89Z4T1w55YkJZzhBTic8Eico6NDoM2exvKefbcVgA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>一、工具</strong></p><p>铅笔，纸，樱花勾线笔，辉柏嘉水溶彩铅</p><p><strong>二、底稿</strong></p><p>先用铅笔画好底稿、</p><p>然后樱花勾线笔进行勾线</p><p>勾完线等笔迹干了之后</p><p>用橡皮擦去铅笔笔迹</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0Hsza1qCzajkMEcIEZYuSicm9DmR9d3Zic5Unk4Mqg9q8JUUD0G8BTkprEw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>三、上色</strong></p><p>用418号平涂小旗子，</p><p>496号灰色画旗杆和冰刀。再用499黑色加深下暗部。</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0HsI3efAAs9GMUgKcvtbg7GiataOsaswOLaSEfm8VRvEmlic2YSjibs6sNJw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;身体用409号铺底色，<br></p><p>再用414号加深边缘部分。注意尾巴有一点渐变的效果。</p><p>马甲用470号嫩绿色平涂</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0HsiaAUywNFWxvr3r7kyjQJCdm7ouKOxC2DAQ9z8uQp8iaTSiaDcKGS96b6w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>再用459号深绿色加深边缘。</p><p>注意深浅色的过渡。</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0HszKWpDUTKbFM8Uv2Ut7ibRibiboZG9ltg3ZCc9WTIRDuAVCVaL5jMJNNsw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>最后加上相框，<br></p><p>拍上几张</p><p>到朋友圈打卡咯</p><p><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0Hs9yqLybRZxktlGXL27YYJ0JqwZESR8R4X6VgohyxgUr7qsJMe8p8YPw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'>&nbsp;</p><p>喜欢吗？</p><p>快来和我一起打卡吧</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;<img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UMDZj3FARlG0kTJDo9Ye1ljBBku9U0HstIpVaq8CMAuiavGh89Z4T1w55YkJZzhBTic8Eico6NDoM2exvKefbcVgA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg'><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;<br></p><p><br></p>",
